<p>This article is about the Christopher Fry play. For the optical phenomenon occasionally seen in the sky, see <ref target="/wiki/22%C2%B0_halo" title="22° halo">22° halo</ref>. For other uses, see <ref class="mw-redirect mw-disambig" href="/wiki/Rings_Around_the_Moon_(disambiguation)" title="Rings Around the Moon (disambiguation)">Rings Around the Moon (disambiguation)</ref>.</p>
